title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Someone close to you may deliver an astute observation about your psyche today that both intrigues and annoys you. Your curiosity blossoms if you intuitively sense theyre hitting the target uncomfortably close to the mark. Nevertheless, you might struggle to understand the point of their message. Taking a bit of quiet time for yourself can help you put everything in proper perspective. Perhaps youre irritated because you perceive that your boundaries are under attack, but remember, youre the final authority of whats true about your life, not anyone else. Do not confuse the voice of ego with that of intuition. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
